5. Create a Python project of a Magic 8 Ball which is a toy used for fortune-telling or seeking advice.

Allow the user to input their question.
Show an in progress message.
Create 10/20 responses, and show a random response.
Allow the user to ask another question/advice or quit the game.


For instance it would look like:


Hello World, I am the Magic 8 Ball, What is your name?
Sara
hello Sara
Ask me a question.
Tell my fortune
It is certain
I hope that helped!
Do you have another question? [Y/N] 
Y
Ask me a question.
My favorite color
My reply is no
I hope that helped!
Do you have another question? [Y/N] 
N
